latestIgtvVideos.title: My everyday go to makeup look by Mousshmi Suvarna
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Once upon a time there was a girl who loved makeup, and then she lost touch with it, but that changes today. 

Today is a big day for me as it’s my Dad’s birthday & my first official upload, needless to say that I’m bloody nervous but just as excited too. I decided to finally go for this kind of Vlogging after mulling over it all through the lockdown (Yes! A little bit of a procrastinator too😋)

I hope my Dad & all you guys love this little gift of passion. This is not just for dad or myself but also for all those people out there who are or have been unsure of taking the first step. Please don’t be, what is the worst that can happen, you will fail right? So what? Try again. Exactly what I plan on doing – KEEP FAILING, KEEP TRYING.

I am not a pro but do hope to get there soon, here I have tried a few things & experiments, hope you like what you see & if you don’t, all your suggestions are more than welcome!

Lots of Love, 
Mousshmi Suvarna

Edit courtesy: @grv_arora ☺️🥂🙏🏻

P.S – Wishing you a very very very happy birthday Dadda. May god always keep you in the bestest of health. I love you the mostest. Even if I become half like you in life, it will be an achievement. Hence restarting on a day, god made legends like you.
